Uber Eats waives delivery fees for over 100 000 independent restaurants,In response to the coronavirus pandemic and its impact on the restaurant industry  Uber Eats is waiving delivery fees for over 100 000 independent restaurants across the US and Canada  It s the latest move by gig economy businesses like Uber  Lyft and Grubhub,Uber Eats is also launching daily marketing campaigns to promote delivery from local restaurants  especially those that are new to the app  It will allow restaurants of all sizes to opt into daily payments on all Uber Eats orders  rather than weekly billing    664 chars 
